{"tid":552810,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無國界記者促停用中國iCloud保私隱","createTime":"2018-02-07T01:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T17:42:03.000Z","uid":51717,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef32f2bdc909e9e56400a47141e688fedaf97512","tid":552810,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180207/20297752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F20297752&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3dd1db3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F20297752&h=efbb8330\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180207/20297752</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果的中國iCloud雲端服務本月28日起由貴州政府全資擁有的雲上貴州公司營運，以法國巴黎為總部的「無國界記者」5日發表聲明，警告記者及博客在該日前停止使用中國的蘋果iCloud或改變用戶區域設定，以保障個人私隱特別是消息人士的安全。<br />\n無國界記者指出，蘋果應用程式使用者大部份的個人資料包括相片、檔案、電郵、互聯網搜尋歷史、地緣資料及密碼，均會在iCloud內儲存，中國的iCloud營運商改由雲上貴州接手營運後，雲上貴州有權查閱用戶資料，將會為新聞工作者及博客的安全及他們消息來源的安全帶來危險，因此，促請記者及博客停用中國的蘋果iCloud雲端服務或改變用戶區域設定。<br />\n<br />\n難確保蘋果不向華洩密<br />\n<br />\n無國界記者組織台北辦事處主任艾瑋昂表示，他們此舉是要保護記者和保護言論自由，對蘋果公司和中國政府已做出的決定，他不期待會有改變。艾瑋昂指出，雖然蘋果承諾永遠不會給政府取得（使用者）內容的後門，但認為蘋果沒辦法確定做到。他表示，鑑於中國政府的決心及對它施壓手法的瞭解，中國即使現在沒有這樣做，早晚也會這樣做。艾瑋昂說，蘋果富可敵國，現金存量幾乎等於芬蘭的國內生產總值，有能力和中國政府討價還價，但蘋果卻只想討好北京"},{"pid":"39b36503e0f66a2273a48b820a2d233b651def90","tid":552810,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"香港記者會唔會表態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca815bd20e5ea36a76093fb9af64b38e274586a","tid":552810,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"香港會唔會都連上大陸Cloud?"},{"pid":"2f18d2c7c4d93b716f42df39d125ca1a7796ec14","tid":552810,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:39:57.000Z","msg":"條死基佬同豬西爭做奶共第一"},{"pid":"799cc5a58601580c269fbe220eb5e816535cb7a9","tid":552810,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca815bd20e5ea36a76093fb9af64b38e274586a","tid":552810,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"香港會唔會都連上大陸Cloud?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"蘋果曾表示，事件只影響內地AppleID用戶，新數據中心不涵蓋香港客戶。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180111/20270833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270833&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=339c934e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270833&h=d5abdb4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180111/20270833</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【教學】中國蘋果 iCloud 轉移上貴州　一按檢查帳戶是否受影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/23/icloudchinaserver/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2Ficloudchinaserver%2Fsoftware%2F&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f4350c77\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/23/icloudchinaserver/software/</a>"},{"pid":"7aa0edc3368f8ed2ec8e04d0b2d0001e02bacb24","tid":552810,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港會唔會都連上大陸Cloud?</blockquote><br />\n現在唔會，遲吓唔知，佢鐘意幾時改都得"},{"pid":"e7d2fbb7a0334b3cfdf9979ff09d54fafe5b8d0e","tid":552810,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa0edc3368f8ed2ec8e04d0b2d0001e02bacb24","tid":552810,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港會唔會都連上大陸Cloud?</blockquote><br />\n現在唔會，遲吓唔知，佢鐘意幾時改都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018